            "description": "<article class=\"post-body\" data-v-1d7d601f=\"\">\n<h3 style=\"text-indent: 0em; text-align: left;\">\n<span style=\"font-family: sans-serif;\">今日看点</span>\n</h3>\n<ul class=\"list-paddingleft-2\" style=\"list-style-type: decimal;\">\n<li>\n<p style=\"text-indent: 0em; text-align: left;\">\n<a href=\"https://data.iyiou.com/intelligence/details/f0b23c25b868f188b86cadbc90e2460e?source=iyiou.dgs\" target=\"_blank\"><strong style=\"font-size: 18px;\">险资密集加仓高股息资产，银行股尤受青睐</strong></a><br/>\n</p>\n<p style=\"text-indent: 0em; text-align: left;display: block;\">\n</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p style=\"text-indent: 0em; text-align: left;\">\n<a href=\"https://data.iyiou.com/intelligence/details/f1fc4adce7c82352385e4fb9e18d6d49?source=iyiou.dgs\" target=\"_blank\"><strong style=\"font-size: 18px;\">网易创新企业大会召开，发布CoreAgent智能体开发平台</strong></a><br/>\n</p>\n<p style=\"text-indent: 0em; text-align: left;display: block;\">\n</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p style=\"text-indent: 0em; text-align: left;\">\n<a href=\"https://data.iyiou.com/intelligence/details/af049777ed996bf9faf3e8f9fa753323?source=iyiou.dgs\" target=\"_blank\"><strong style=\"font-size: 18px;\">全球短剧迎来爆发性增长   机构关注AI及出海新方向</strong></a><br/>\n</p>\n<p style=\"text-indent: 0em; text-align: left;display: block;\">\n</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p style=\"margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt; font-size:11pt\">\n<br/>\n</p>\n<h3 style=\"text-indent: 0em; text-align: left;\">\n        今日情报（16家15条）\n    </h3>\n<ul class=\"list-paddingleft-2\" style=\"list-style-type: disc;\">\n<li>\n<p style=\"text-indent: 0em; text-align: left;\">\n<span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong>\n<a href=\"https://data.iyiou.com/company/details/75374e0c26bb9b378a48e586bf527db2/profile?source=iyiou.dgs\" target=\"_blank\">中国平安</a>\n</strong></span>\n</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p style=\"text-indent: 0em; text-align: left;\">\n<a href=\"https://data.iyiou.com/intelligence/details/f0b23c25b868f188b86cadbc90e2460e?source=iyiou.dgs\" target=\"_blank\">险资密集加仓高股息资产，银行股尤受青睐</a>\n</p>\n<ul class=\"list-paddingleft-2\" style=\"list-style-type: disc;\">\n<li>\n<p style=\"text-indent: 0em; text-align: left;\">\n<span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong>\n<a href=\"https://data.iyiou.com/company/details/42e54d59b38ee210021c5957a3ecb2db/profile?source=iyiou.dgs\" target=\"_blank\">网易</a>\n</strong></span>\n</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p style=\"text-indent: 0em; text-align: left;\">\n<a href=\"https://data.iyiou.com/intelligence/details/f1fc4adce7c82352385e4fb9e18d6d49?source=iyiou.dgs\" target=\"_blank\">网易创新企业大会召开，发布CoreAgent智能体开发平台</a>\n</p>\n<ul class=\"list-paddingleft-2\" style=\"list-style-type: disc;\">\n<li>\n<p style=\"text-indent: 0em; text-align: left;\">\n<span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong>\n<a href=\"https://data.iyiou.com/company/details/a14b9ec6082c8e1700f4f42d75d84e79/profile?source=iyiou.dgs\" target=\"_blank\">美团</a>，<a href=\"https://data.iyiou.com/company/details/44359e4b8ffbd515671c0414418988c7/profile?source=iyiou.dgs\" target=\"_blank\">携程</a>\n</strong></span>\n</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p style=\"text-indent: 0em; text-align: left;\">\n<a href=\"https://data.iyiou.com/intelligence/details/af049777ed996bf9faf3e8f9fa753323?source=iyiou.dgs\" target=\"_blank\">全球短剧迎来爆发性增长   机构关注AI及出海新方向</a>\n</p>\n<ul class=\"list-paddingleft-2\" style=\"list-style-type: disc;\">\n<li>\n<p style=\"text-indent: 0em; text-align: left;\">\n<span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong>\n<a href=\"https://data.iyiou.com/company/details/463f19d5f3476dd5ec65bfd48ca61223/profile?source=iyiou.dgs\" target=\"_blank\">阿里巴巴</a>\n</strong></span>\n</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p style=\"text-indent: 0em; text-align: left;\">\n<a href=\"https://data.iyiou.com/intelligence/details/fdd7d5584b77b8728a147270a2734876?source=iyiou.dgs\" target=\"_blank\"> 阿里影业(01060)涨近6% 公司拟更名为大麦娱乐 花旗称IP商品潜力尚未完全释放</a>\n</p>\n<ul class=\"list-paddingleft-2\" style=\"list-style-type: disc;\">\n<li>\n<p style=\"text-indent: 0em; text-align: left;\">\n<span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong>\n<a href=\"https://data.iyiou.com/company/details/733fdf5cb2f803f31afda052434133eb/profile?source=iyiou.dgs\" target=\"_blank\">恒瑞医药</a>\n</strong></span>\n</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p style=\"text-indent: 0em; text-align: left;\">\n<a href=\"https://data.iyiou.com/intelligence/details/ecb6bff146edac7f3f95553162348c6b?source=iyiou.dgs\" target=\"_blank\">恒瑞医药在港上市，创新药出海能否追上百济神州？</a>\n</p>\n<ul class=\"list-paddingleft-2\" style=\"list-style-type: disc;\">\n<li>\n<p style=\"text-indent: 0em; text-align: left;\">\n<span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong>\n<a href=\"https://data.iyiou.com/company/details/f95ce8317b68d8b5ec79af35c6abf9d9/profile?source=iyiou.dgs\" target=\"_blank\">中国联通</a>\n</strong></span>\n</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p style=\"text-indent: 0em; text-align: left;\">\n<a href=\"https://data.iyiou.com/intelligence/details/493cc160a338288efa860fd4a2af883c?source=iyiou.dgs\" target=\"_blank\">佳源科技深交所创业板IPO“终止”</a>\n</p>\n<ul class=\"list-paddingleft-2\" style=\"list-style-type: disc;\">\n<li>\n<p style=\"text-indent: 0em; text-align: left;\">\n<span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong>\n<a href=\"https://data.iyiou.com/company/details/fc54a3643978749f2dd0b3d5947d99f7/profile?source=iyiou.dgs\" target=\"_blank\">韦尔股份</a>\n</strong></span>\n</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p style=\"text-indent: 0em; text-align: left;\">\n<a href=\"https://data.iyiou.com/intelligence/details/574227bdafa582ec2a9390be31b690f3?source=iyiou.dgs\" target=\"_blank\">韦尔股份：拟发行H股股票并在香港联合交易所有限公司上市</a>\n</p>\n<ul class=\"list-paddingleft-2\" style=\"list-style-type: disc;\">\n<li>\n<p style=\"text-indent: 0em; text-align: left;\">\n<span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong>\n<a href=\"https://data.iyiou.com/company/details/975067db32ecf69157dcde35add6a415/profile?source=iyiou.dgs\" target=\"_blank\">小鹏汽车</a>\n</strong></span>\n</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p style=\"text-indent: 0em; text-align: left;\">\n<a href=\"https://data.iyiou.com/intelligence/details/03efe808f95126c0d7d140adceb0a317?source=iyiou.dgs\" target=\"_blank\">财联社5月23日电，小鹏汽车联席总裁顾宏地接受采访时表示，小鹏汽车希望在2026年向消费者推出飞行汽车产品。</a>\n</p>\n<ul class=\"list-paddingleft-2\" style=\"list-style-type: disc;\">\n<li>\n<p style=\"text-indent: 0em; text-align: left;\">\n<span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong>\n<a href=\"https://data.iyiou.com/company/details/33e222bf363f606f60ad70903f051c06/profile?source=iyiou.dgs\" target=\"_blank\">小马智行</a>\n</strong></span>\n</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p style=\"text-indent: 0em; text-align: left;\">\n<a href=\"https://data.iyiou.com/intelligence/details/dd39a7cabc1eb81c7f3b00cda1c983af?source=iyiou.dgs\" target=\"_blank\"> 速腾聚创(02498)再涨超8% 与库犸科技达成战略合作 首批订单三年内合作120万台</a>\n</p>\n<ul class=\"list-paddingleft-2\" style=\"list-style-type: disc;\">\n<li>\n<p style=\"text-indent: 0em; text-align: left;\">\n<span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong>\n<a href=\"https://data.iyiou.com/company/details/2b294d039331b81bc235a568f854522b/profile?source=iyiou.dgs\" target=\"_blank\">中国通号</a>\n</strong></span>\n</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p style=\"text-indent: 0em; text-align: left;\">\n<a href=\"https://data.iyiou.com/intelligence/details/a753d8afb9f6a08f37eb9093f6965269?source=iyiou.dgs\" target=\"_blank\">中国通号(688009.SH)：3至4月合计中标约37.89亿元重要项目</a>\n</p>\n<ul class=\"list-paddingleft-2\" style=\"list-style-type: disc;\">\n<li>\n<p style=\"text-indent: 0em; text-align: left;\">\n<span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong>\n<a href=\"https://data.iyiou.com/company/details/ebc8bca9a86dfdd1e79cd51575767af3/profile?source=iyiou.dgs\" target=\"_blank\">华海药业</a>\n</strong></span>\n</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p style=\"text-indent: 0em; text-align: left;\">\n<a href=\"https://data.iyiou.com/intelligence/details/20bb052a6971d2ed8f66ec9ccd69cd38?source=iyiou.dgs\" target=\"_blank\">华海药业(600521.SH)子公司获批开展注射用HB0043 I期临床试验</a>\n</p>\n<ul class=\"list-paddingleft-2\" style=\"list-style-type: disc;\">\n<li>\n<p style=\"text-indent: 0em; text-align: left;\">\n<span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong>\n<a href=\"https://data.iyiou.com/company/details/0eadf18647bfda65cb8f8fadfa074c54/profile?source=iyiou.dgs\" target=\"_blank\">百润股份</a>\n</strong></span>\n</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p style=\"text-indent: 0em; text-align: left;\">\n<a href=\"https://data.iyiou.com/intelligence/details/6df1157ead3dc67d0c4ad23b323b39aa?source=iyiou.dgs\" target=\"_blank\">方正证券：智能眼镜有望成为端侧AI落地最佳场景之一 AI+AR眼镜有望快速发展</a>\n</p>\n<ul class=\"list-paddingleft-2\" style=\"list-style-type: disc;\">\n<li>\n<p style=\"text-indent: 0em; text-align: left;\">\n<span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong>\n<a href=\"https://data.iyiou.com/company/details/ea1615e0572aa1ee7b3a09dcec7689a4/profile?source=iyiou.dgs\" target=\"_blank\">滔搏</a>\n</strong></span>\n</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p style=\"text-indent: 0em; text-align: left;\">\n<a href=\"https://data.iyiou.com/intelligence/details/bda5a28b126119ff6aa5e88783c11480?source=iyiou.dgs\" target=\"_blank\"> 滔搏(06110)跌超6% 机构指去库存背景下折扣加深拖累公司毛利率表现</a>\n</p>\n<ul class=\"list-paddingleft-2\" style=\"list-style-type: disc;\">\n<li>\n<p style=\"text-indent: 0em; text-align: left;\">\n<span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong>\n<a href=\"https://data.iyiou.com/company/details/c050d3260b4e40a08026ddf79aada4d4/profile?source=iyiou.dgs\" target=\"_blank\">高鑫零售</a>\n</strong></span>\n</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p style=\"text-indent: 0em; text-align: left;\">\n<a href=\"https://data.iyiou.com/intelligence/details/0867a4017e3c81fd77d90da581ce17c3?source=iyiou.dgs\" target=\"_blank\">高鑫零售(06808)拟委任毕马威为新任核数师</a>\n</p>\n<ul class=\"list-paddingleft-2\" style=\"list-style-type: disc;\">\n<li>\n<p style=\"text-indent: 0em; text-align: left;\">\n<span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong>\n<a href=\"https://data.iyiou.com/company/details/97226f108cca31a28662a6846a8bcace/profile?source=iyiou.dgs\" target=\"_blank\">中国诚通</a>\n</strong></span>\n</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p style=\"text-indent: 0em; text-align: left;\">\n<a href=\"https://data.iyiou.com/intelligence/details/6dde50427515f98567fc9d757efedd35?source=iyiou.dgs\" target=\"_blank\">“国家队”参与国